    </p>

    <a href="mailto:matthew@mimhoff.com"
      class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 text-white px-5 py-2.5 rounded font-bold uppercase tracking-wider text-sm transition-colors mb-10"
      style="background-color: #c0392b; box-shadow: 0 2px 8px rgba(192,57,43,0.4);" onmouseover="this.style.backgroundColor='#e04444'" onmouseout="this.style.backgroundColor='#c0392b'">
